      <title>新加坡华侨银行加强对国际客户的审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/singapore-bank-ocbc-tightens-scrutiny-on-international-clients</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡第二大银行华侨银行要求一些国际客户出示居住在新加坡的证明，以免他们的账户被关闭，这是在一系列洗钱案件发生后，银行加强审查的信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/singapore-bank-ocbc-tightens-scrutiny-on-international-clients</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 09:44:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国电力公司上调2024年核电发电量目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/edf-raises-target-for-2024-nuclear-power-production-in-france</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国电力公司今年第二次上调了法国核电产量目标，理由是该公司在管理电厂维护停机以及破裂管道的检查和修复方面取得了进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/edf-raises-target-for-2024-nuclear-power-production-in-france</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 08:24:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>通胀数据比市场显示的更重要</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/inflation-reading-matters-more-than-the-equity-market-is-showing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[虽然抗通胀的斗争可能基本取得了胜利，但价格压力带来的紧张局势仍可能破坏人们对降息的信心。股市似乎对这些警告视而不见。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/inflation-reading-matters-more-than-the-equity-market-is-showing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 08:13:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰能源公司 Orlen 因成本飙升取消重要石化项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/polish-refiner-orlen-scraps-key-petrochemical-project-on-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰 Orlen SA 削减了其最大的石化项目投资，原因是建设成本上涨了六倍多，将项目规模缩小为主要基于已建成的基础设施。该公司股价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/polish-refiner-orlen-scraps-key-petrochemical-project-on-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 07:54:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
